org.chronos.chronodb.internal.impl.query.parser.ast

Interface QueryElement

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryOperatorElement, DoubleWhereElement, LongWhereElement, NotElement, StringWhereElement, WhereElement

    public interface QueryElement
    A QueryElement represents a single element in the Abstract Syntax Tree (AST) of a ChronoDBQuery.

    Please note that all instances of classes that implement this interface are assumed to be immutable.
